ith shavings, chips, shingles, broken halves of bricks, and freshly turned earth, indicating recent construction activity.&#10;&#10;Overall, the newly built house boasts an impressive and distinctive appearance, with its unique gables and architectural details, while also exuding a sense of history and character that sets it apart from its more modern neighbors.">
